al reducible unitary\nrepresentation of this nilpotent algebra, which is then decomposed using its\nCasimir operators.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Nov 2021 11:29:52 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 11 Mar 2022 04:11:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-14"}
