nce on treewidth when $\\Delta < 2t$ or when $q < 4t$ and $\\Delta < t^2$.\n  We additionally show that the Glauber dynamics on the partial $q$-colorings\nof $G$ mix rapidly for all $\\lambda > 0$ when $q \\geq \\Delta + 2$ is bounded.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Nov 2021 14:54:28 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-09"}
