ion, even if the\ninterstellar C/H, Si/H, Mg/H and Fe/H abundances are assumed to be proto-solar\nabundances augmented by Galactic chemical evolution.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 6 Nov 2021 15:27:33 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-22"}
